Effective Date: July 12, 2025

Thank you for using our Laundry App ("we", "our", or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information
Name
Phone number
Contact details

b. Service Information
Laundry service types

Service history (e.g. weight, price, payment status, claim status)

Add-ons or instructions provided

c. Usage Data
App usage patterns (e.g. screen views, features used)

Technical data (e.g. device type, operating system)

üîí We do NOT collect passwords, GPS location, or access your photos, files, or messages.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:

Record and manage laundry service transactions

Maintain customer service history

Show summaries such as income reports and pending collections

Improve our app features and user experience

3. Data Storage
Your data is securely stored locally on your device using SQLite.

We do not send your data to remote servers or third-party providers.

4. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties. Your data stays private and is only used within the app.

5. Data Security
We use industry-standard practices to protect your data, including:

Device-level encryption

Local-only data access (no internet sync unless you enable it in the future)

6. Your Rights
You have the right to:

View your data

Delete customer records manually through the app

Contact us if you wish to fully delete all app data

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we will notify you in the app.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:

